ARP: Antenna Reference Point
    L1 : L1 Phase Center                   L2 : L2 Phase Center
    BAM: bottom of antenna mount           BPA: bottom of preamplifier
    BCR: bottom of chokering	           TCR: top of chokering
NRP:North Reference Point   
    RXC:receiver connector (connect antenna to external receiver)  

All dimensions are in meters.